article.description: Kayla McBride had 14 points and six rebounds, Natalie Novosel added 13 points and No. 12 Notre Dame routed Morehead State 91-28 Monday night.
article.headline: Kayla McBride had leads way as Notre Dame wins by 63
article.linkText: Notre Dame routs Morehead State by 63 points
article.story:
SOUTH BEND, Ind. --  Kayla McBride had 14 points and six rebounds, Natalie Novosel added 13 points and No. 12 Notre Dame routed Morehead State 91-28 Monday night.

McBride finished a miss by junior forward Erica Solomon with 11:44 remaining in the first half to give the Irish an 18-2 lead. The Eagles were held to seven points in the first half on 2 for 20 shooting.

Natalie Achonwa and Kaila Turner each scored 10 points for Notre Dame (2-0). Sophomore preseason All-American Skylar Diggins had nine points and eight assists, one shy of her career high.

Chynna Bozeman led with Morehead State (0-2) with 12 points, but she had 10 turnovers.
